 9. Enable BoradCast Providers
10. php artisan serve
11. http://127.0.0.1:8000/laravel-websockets
12. php artisan make:event testWebSocket
13. Change Chanel name
14. Change bootstrap file
15. npm install laravel-echo pusher-js
16. npm install
17. npm  run dev
18. create file for listener checkWebSocket
19. Then http://127.0.0.1:8000/trigger-event hit from this event
20. Get Listen from http://127.0.0.1:8000/listening-event
